description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you experienced in providing Complex Care to children and young people?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Apollo Home Healthcare is seeking experienced Health Care Assistants to support a young girl with complex care needs at her family home in Darlington.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; We are looking for dedicated and compassionate Health Care Assistants who are passionate about their job, enjoy delivering one to one support and who can build positive relationships with our service users and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our service user is a young girl who is registered deaf and blind, sensory stimulation and play time will be a big part of your role. It is important for her care team to engage and get involved in everything she enjoys.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the day, her favourite thing to do is hand-painting, playing with her playdough and soft sensory toys and spending quality time with her family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Night shifts will involve you getting our service user settled for the night and assisting with her bed time routine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 months previous care experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medication Administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal Care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moving and Handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seizure Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ventilation Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PEG Feeding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have the following shifts available;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Part Time Days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Night shifts from 9:30pm to 8:30am&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This is a personally rewarding role where you can build on your clinical skills and experience, whilst delivering exceptional care and support to our service user and really making an impact on her day to day life.&lt;/p&gt;
